Step 5:
Interfacing LCD 16x2 Display (I2C)

{
The LCD 16x2 display will show real-time values from the DHT11, Rain Sensor, BMP180, and MQ-2 sensors. 
}

LCD with I2C Module 


Connections for I2C LCD:
>I2C LCD Pin	Arduino Pin
>VCC	5V
>GND	GND
>SDA	A4
>SCL	A5


......Install the I2C Library:
 install the LiquidCrystal_I2C library:
...............Open Arduino IDE
                Go to Sketch → Include Library → Manage Libraries
                Search for LiquidCrystal_I2C and install it.
